Group port: 10-20pp old world, 30-50pp Kunark, 40-100pp Velious<br>
Translocate: going rate seems to be 25pp ... punts to other places may cost more because they require a reagent that costs a couple of plat and is only buyable in Temple of Sol Ro<br>
SoW: You can usually get one of these without charge, but a donation of 2pp is reasonable and will usually be accepted<br>
Rez: Depends on level of res, level of cleric, what the cleric was busy doing, and whether cleric has click stick.  Depending on these things, anywhere from free up to 300pp (the 300pp charge I saw was because the cleric was busy doing something else in a fairly far away zone) ... I usually try to donate about 50pp if I get rezzed by a non-clicking cleric.<br>
<br>
Generally, services cost more if they interrupt what the person is doing, if the person providing the service is high level, and if it uses more of the person's time.  A level 29 druid may port to WC for 10pp, but at level 58 I generally don't do ports for less than 50pp, and usually not even then. <p><font face="Verdana, Arial" size="2">
Katlynel Wolfcaller
<BR>58 Preserver, Saryrn
<BR>170 Tailor - 181 Fletcher - 175 Jeweler - 174 Potter - 168 Brewer - 163 Baker - 151 Blacksmith - 126 Fisher
</font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/uaren31.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aren31</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 216<br> <font color=#DDA0DD>(8/3/01 4:32:50 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Prices for services??</span><hr size=1> I'm not a cleric but I'd look at rez charges like this.<br>
<br>
If your corpse is in the same zone as me and you drag to me, No Charge.<br>
<br>
If rezzing you requires going into another zone, charge 100pp<br>
<br>
If I need to cross an entire zone and zone twice, 200pp<br>
<br>
And for every time I need to cross a zone line, add 100pp<br>
<br>
So if your dead in Steamfont, and I'm in Dragon Necropolis, and no one is there to port, you better be uber rich if I'm gonna run accross the world to rez you.<br>
<br>
This is considering a 49 rez and again I'm not a cleric so what do I know.<br>
<br>
Sow shold be free, but 1-2pp donation is always good if you can afford it.<br>
<br>
Ports: Depends how bad I want to get where I'm going.<br>
Not too much rush I'll offer 10-20pp, If I want to get there faster 30-50pp, and the one time I needed to be somewhere NOW I offered 100pp for the port, and Not one person would port me despite there being 15 druids and wizzies in OT, I ran all the way to DL shouting &quot;100p for a port&quot; before someone could port me. <p>Aren Steelblade<BR>
